00:44:16,140 --> 00:44:20,180
and do it fairly quickly without a lot of,

863
00:44:20,180 --> 00:44:22,340
you know, debate and discussion.

864
00:44:24,580 --> 00:44:29,580
And I think that's the thing that I'm sort of most anxious

