01:18:01,880 --> 01:18:05,040
There is a complimentary aspect

1514
01:18:05,040 --> 01:18:07,580
to this question of consumer flexibility

1515
01:18:07,580 --> 01:18:09,780
and that is the question of flexibility

1516
01:18:09,780 --> 01:18:11,120
on the side of producers

1517
01:18:11,120 --> 01:18:14,480
because another thing that the Austrians brought forward

1518
01:18:14,480 --> 01:18:16,240
and you mentioned them already

1519
