01:18:43,820 --> 01:18:48,820
How is it being decided whether or not resources

1527
01:18:49,520 --> 01:18:53,440
can be allocated sensibly into a direction

1528
01:18:53,440 --> 01:18:57,720
which might not be like fully developed

1529
01:18:57,720 --> 01:19:00,540
where the odds are not clear

1530
01:19:00,540 --> 01:19:03,660
whether or not something might succeed or not.

1531
01:19:03,660 --> 01:19:07,260
So how is all of this being decided upon?

